OL,3,CGang convicted over #200m money
OL,4,Claundering plot
OL,6,FFour men have been convicted over a
OL,7,F#200 million plot to turn criminal
OL,8,Fcash into untraceable gold.
OL,10,FA jury sitting at Leeds Crown Court
OL,11,Ffound Gregory Frankel, 47, Daniel
OL,12,FRawson, 47, Haroon Rashid, 54, and
OL,13,FArjun Babber, 32, guilty of money
OL,14,Flaundering.
OL,16,FJames Stunt, the former son-in-law of
OL,17,FBritish F1 tycoon Bernie Ecclestone,
OL,18,Fwas acquitted of the charges.
