OL,3,CGang convicted over #200m money
OL,4,Claundering plot
OL,6,FThe trial heard that between 2014 and
OL,7,F2016, cash was brought from across the
OL,8,Fcountry to Bradford gold dealer Fowler
OL,9,FOldfield as well as Mr Stunt's
OL,10,Fbusiness premises in London and the
OL,11,Foffice of a company called Pure Nines
OL,12,FLimited in Hatton Garden, central
OL,13,FLondon.
OL,15,FThe defendants were accused of hiding
OL,16,Fthe origin of the money by laundering
OL,17,Fit through a company bank account and
OL,18,Fusing the proceeds to buy gold which
OL,19,Fwas shipped to Dubai.
