OL,3,CGang convicted over #200m money
OL,4,Claundering plot
OL,6,FCCTV footage showed couriers from as
OL,7,Ffar afield as Glasgow, Manchester and
OL,8,FMerseyside arriving at Hall Lane,
OL,9,FBradford, carrying heavy bags laden
OL,10,Fwith bank notes.
OL,12,FAt one stage, an average of #1.7
OL,13,Fmillion a day in cash was coming into
OL,14,Fthe premises in sports bags, carrier
OL,15,Fbags, 'bags for life', gift-wrapped
OL,16,Ftoy boxes and even take-away food
OL,17,Fcontainers.
