OL,4,Claundering plot
OL,6,FIt was counted on professional money-
OL,7,Fcounting machines and collected by
OL,8,Flegitimate cash-in-transit companies
OL,9,Fto deposit into a bank.
OL,11,FWest Yorkshire Police's economic crime
OL,12,Funit was alerted in 2016 when a cash-
OL,13,Fin-transit company raised concerns
OL,14,Fabout the huge increase in cash being
OL,15,Fcollected from Fowler Oldfield.
