OL,3,CGang convicted over #200m money
OL,4,Claundering plot
OL,6,FInvestigators carried out surveillance
OL,7,Fon the property and discovered
OL,8,Fcriminal cash was arriving to be
OL,9,Fcounted and banked.
OL,11,FThe West Yorkshire Police probe found
OL,12,Fthat, from 2014 onwards, Fowler
OL,13,FOldfield saw a substantial increase in
OL,14,Fthe amount of cash paid into its
OL,15,Faccounts, from just over #11,000 in
OL,16,F2012 to over #650,000 a year later.
OL,18,FBy 2015, payments into the long-
OL,19,Festablished Bradford company had grown
OL,20,Fto #95million.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/9
