OL,3,CGang convicted over #200m money
OL,4,Claundering plot
OL,6,FAt times the amount of cash being
OL,7,Fbanked by the company in a single day
OL,8,Fwas said to be similar to that taken
OL,9,Fby a Premier League football club
OL,10,Ffollowing a big match.
OL,12,FJonathan Sandiford KC, prosecuting,
OL,13,Ftold the jury how Frankel and Rawson
OL,14,Fwere the owners of Bradford jewellers
OL,15,FFowler Oldfield.
OL,17,FFourteen of the couriers who were seen
OL,18,Fon CCTV delivering cash to Fowler
OL,19,FOldfield were convicted of money
OL,20,Flaundering offences in earlier trials.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/9
